5bb95fd","tid":215953,"uid":70240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要做d客想投資整生意既business plan 然後你要幫客執番好 仲要同佢搞埋銀行申請 一句睇你做咩公司啦 睇你公司好冇景<br />\n<br />\n利申 之前係wall street做呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間？d大客係咪去晒Mk/boston/bain</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGreater China黎計大客都係McK同BCG食哂<br />\nOW都有唔少大客<br />\nBain應該係最霉嗰間"},{"pid":"9454b73d7cf5a1c279922e499bbc89737a39b0be","tid":215953,"uid":25080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"點入行？"},{"pid":"b9e25d68f3dbd4a82a92415d716be580e70fa271","tid":215953,"uid":71258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點入行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuper high GPA<br />\n<br />\nInternships<br />\n<br />\nFrom overseas unis or MBAs<br />\n<br />\nQuite difficult for students from HK now because they like hiring mainlanders"},{"pid":"b88d4b4f0970985f6df6cc997b8b1e01c3bddedb","tid":215953,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"Big 4 唔可以叫做consulting 佢自己都自稱Advisory<br />\n<br />\n歷史計落 Big4 得DTT 血純比較純正， 其他都係買下賣下再Rebuild返出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲有乜想知?"},{"pid":"2305c8e8abe232258ad86f272af360c28230fa4c","tid":215953,"uid":71258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點入行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuper high GPA<br />\n<br />\nInternships<br />\n<br />\nFrom overseas unis or MBAs<br />\n<br />\nQuite difficult for students from HK now because they like hiring mainlanders who study in HK[/size=3]</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nFor overseas unis they like hiring from Ivy League, Oxbridge.<br />\n<br />\nTo prepare for interviews, master your skills in case interviews first, taking a look at <a href=\"http://www.caseinterview.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caseinterview.com%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=67e58d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.caseinterview.com/</a> by Victor Cheng. It's a must."},{"pid":"565723f69fc805760772b2e41342c8037e6ed63c","tid":215953,"uid":71258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點入行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuper high GPA<br />\n<br />\nInternships<br />\n<br />\nFrom overseas unis or MBAs<br />\n<br />\nQuite difficult for students from HK now because they like hiring mainlanders who study in HK[/size=3]</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nFor overseas unis they like hiring from Ivy League, Oxbridge.<br />\n<br />\nTo prepare for interviews, master your skills in case interviews first, taking a look at <a href=\"http://www.caseinterview.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caseinterview.com%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=67e58d91\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caseinterview.com/</a> by Victor Cheng. It's a must.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTo understand what management consultants do, watch this video on YouTube: those who have worked in this industry before will definitely crack up <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=4cyvmF7GD8o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4cyvmF7GD8o&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ffb4d089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=4cyvmF7GD8o</a>"},{"pid":"38fecdbf487d735ced7123f14afbe62532f044d8","tid":215953,"uid":78922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Big 4 唔可以叫做consulting 佢自己都自稱Advisory<br />\n<br />\n歷史計落 Big4 得DTT 血純比較純正， 其他都係買下賣下再Rebuild返出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲有乜想知?</blockquote><br />\n如果fresh grad入pwc做consulting/ advisory<br />\n有冇機會跳入mbb...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bd6530b70c2c4699099a043eb7b72f95c714bf","tid":215953,"uid":74792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61925a1b20662e7cefff6e7b2b54893757c45ebf","tid":215953,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Big 4 唔可以叫做consulting 佢自己都自稱Advisory<br />\n<br />\n歷史計落 Big4 得DTT 血純比較純正， 其他都係買下賣下再Rebuild返出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲有乜想知?</blockquote><br />\n無記得dtt consulting係 收購行內一間一線中至尾既公司 而developed</blockquote><br />\nP記都係收購左間咩O&amp;S先開始做大"},{"pid":"dc5b42e6dbbfb105cd9a325df98d601c5f4e0f8e","tid":215953,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Big 4 唔可以叫做consulting 佢自己都自稱Advisory<br />\n<br />\n歷史計落 Big4 得DTT 血純比較純正， 其他都係買下賣下再Rebuild返出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲有乜想知?</blockquote><br />\n如果fresh grad入pwc做consulting/ advisory<br />\n有冇機會跳入mbb...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 除非你Quit 左 之後讀MBA"},{"pid":"356575e671ba6d1481b3fc9013e3a6be6a397e2a","tid":215953,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Big 4 唔可以叫做consulting 佢自己都自稱Advisory<br />\n<br />\n歷史計落 Big4 得DTT 血純比較純正， 其他都係買下賣下再Rebuild返出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲有乜想知?</blockquote><br />\n無記得dtt consulting係 收購行內一間一線中至尾既公司 而developed</blockquote><br />\n你睇返02年Enron Scandal. 3間big 4 賣曬consulting 公司出去<br />\n<br />\n比如IBM GBS咪係買PwC consulting.<br />\n幾年後咪又自己搞返起 再買其他公司"},{"pid":"c2cf049d48baa35d3dea5e9c74222d32e34f8561","tid":215953,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"其實我唔d公司搵呢d management consulting firm做咩？錢多得濟無掟駛定內部人唔想孭鑊搵街外人做？"},{"pid":"c5489709bf9004bd6cf8dc74fdafd02